Hello! Welcome to Pincho!
#########################

#INSTALLATION: Latest Ubuntu LTS 20.04 Focal Fossa
##################################################

Open terminal in Pincho_Vxx_Master folder and run:
$P_installer.py

The terminal will prompt 'y' or 'n' responses, so stay nearby and answer with 'y'.

At the end the terminal will bring up vdb-config UI, 'enable' and 'exit'. Then you are done with installation! Congrats!

#RUNNING PINCHO:
###################################################

***GOOD HOUSEKEEPING***
Create a new folder (i.e. Files_to_be_processed).

Enter that folder.

Create subfolder(s) with the Species Name and Info as the Folder Name. (i.e. Files_to_be_processed/Pristimantis_toftae_skin_dorsal)

Place respective information to process in those files (i.e. NGS reads F and/or R).

Launch Pincho in parent folder (i.e. Files_to_be_processed)

Reset page.

Select the desired settings.